      "@type": "asbval:ClaimAssessment",
      "asbval:evidence_quote": "The data augmentation module on the DeepION architecture is applied to create modified copies of the existing ion images with some minor changes, facilitating self-supervised training of the DeepION model. The encoder module is used to learn an ion image representation function f(\u2022|\u03b8f) to extract the high-level features from ion images for downstream tasks.",
